this_title: Gareth Reynolds: England, Weed & The Rest
introduction: Gareth Reynolds is an American-British comedian, producer, writer, and podcaster. He is best known for co-hosting The Dollop, a comedy podcast in which his friend and fellow comedian Dave Anthony tells him a particularly shocking or notable story from American history about which Reynolds knows nothing.Captured live at Helium Comedy Club in Portland, OR, "England Weed & The Rest," showcases his signature wit and humor while delving into the peculiarities of being raised by Brits in the US. Join the side-splitting journey through Reynolds' comedic lens, exploring the quirks and intricacies of modern society in a way only he can deliver.
